Package: firefox-3.7-branding
Architecture: any
Depends: firefox-3.7 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Conflicts: abrowser-3.7-branding
Replaces: kubuntu-firefox-installer
Description: Package that ships the firefox branding
 This package ships the Firefox branding bits. If you remove this package your
 user experience will become that of the abrowser.

Package: firefox-3.7-gnome-support
